#

Rich Red Wine Braised Beef with Herb-Infused Mushroom Gravy

$45
800 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

HeartyComfort FoodGourmet

Description

Tender beef braised in rich red wine, served with a savory mushroom gravy infused with aromatic herbs.

Ingredients

  • Beef Chuck Roast: 3 lbs
  • Red Wine: 2 cups
  • Beef Broth: 1 cup
  • Mushrooms (Cremini or Button): 2 cups, sliced
  • Onion: 1 large, diced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Fresh Thyme: 2 tsp, chopped
  • Fresh Rosemary: 1 tsp, chopped
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Bay Leaf: 1
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
